      f_initvars_menu_app
      until [ $MMA -eq 0 ]
      do    # Start of Mathematic Applications until loop.
            #MMA axiom          - General purpose computer algebra system.
            #MMA dicelab        - evaluate the statistical distribution of dice rolls.
            #MMA mathomatic     - Portable CAS (Computer Algebra System)
            #MMA ministat       - Fundamental statistical comparison of 1 or 2 data sets.
            #MMA num-utils      - Collection of programs; avg, normal, random, range, etc.
            #MMA open-axiom     - Open scientific computation platform.
            #MMA plotutils      - Plot 2-dimensional scientific data.
            #MMA pi             - Calculate Archimedes constant Pi to arbitrary precision.
            #MMA primes         - Prime number calculator.
            #MMA pspp           - Statistical analysis tool.
            #MMA relational-cli - relational algebra and relational database.
